snippet.title: RAT ON THE RUN - Gameplay [Donut Games - Collectors ID #07]
snippet.description:
Fill Ratty's growling stomach in Donut Games' classic platformer Rat On The Run.

The video shows gameplay from level 53 "Flaming Floor", one of the new levels shipped with version 1.35

App Store - https://apps.apple.com/app/rat-on-the-run/id321366355
Google Play - https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.donutgames.ratontherun
